OL,3,CScottish Greens call for block on
OL,4,Cgender Bill to be lifted
OL,6,FThe Scottish Greens have called on the
OL,7,FUK Government to remove the block on
OL,8,FScotland's gender reforms.
OL,10,FThe Gender Recognition Reform
OL,11,F(Scotland) Bill was passed at Holyrood
OL,12,Fin 2022, with MSPs backing the plans
OL,13,Fto make it easier for trans people to
OL,14,Fobtain a gender recognition
OL,15,Fcertificate by removing the need for a
OL,16,Fmedical diagnosis.
OL,18,FThe controversial legislation caused a
OL,19,Fpolitical firestorm in Scotland, with
OL,20,Fopponents claiming it could endanger
OL,21,Fwomen's rights.
