OL,3,CScottish Greens call for block on
OL,4,Cgender Bill to be lifted
OL,6,FDespite receiving support from the
OL,7,Fmajority of MSPs in Holyrood, former
OL,8,FScottish secretary Sir Alister Jack
OL,9,Fstepped in and, using Section 35 of
OL,10,Fthe Scotland Act for the first time,
OL,11,Fblocked the legislation from gaining
OL,12,FRoyal Assent and becoming law over
OL,13,Ffears it could impact on UK-wide
OL,14,Fequalities legislation.
OL,16,FThe Scottish Government fought the
OL,17,Fdecision, with the UK Supreme Court
OL,18,Fdeeming it to have been within the law.
