OL,3,CScottish Greens call for block on
OL,4,Cgender Bill to be lifted
OL,6,FSpeaking on the first day of LGBT
OL,7,Fhistory month, Scottish Green
OL,8,Fequalities spokeswoman Maggie Chapman
OL,9,Fsaid: "I urge the Secretary of State
OL,10,Ffor Scotland and his Labour colleagues
OL,11,Fat Westminster to live up to these
OL,12,Fvalues and undo the unfair and
OL,13,Fundemocratic veto on gender
OL,14,Frecognition reform.
OL,16,F"Gender recognition reform was
OL,17,Fsupported by MSPs from all parties,
OL,18,Fincluding the Scottish Labour
OL,19,Fleadership.
