OL,6,F"Upholding the Tory veto undermines
OL,7,Fthe cross-party support that it
OL,8,Freceived and the backing by almost
OL,9,Fevery reputable equalities
OL,10,Forganisation.
OL,12,F"Most importantly, it highlights the
OL,13,Flack of respect offered to some of the
OL,14,Fmost marginalised and frequently
OL,15,Ftargeted communities across Scotland.
