OL,3,CScottish Greens call for block on
OL,4,Cgender Bill to be lifted
OL,6,F"Self-identification is a normal
OL,7,Fprocess that is used in countries
OL,8,Facross the world. Finally allowing it
OL,9,Fto be implemented would be a small
OL,10,Fchange that would offer more hope and
OL,11,Fsupport for a small and marginalised
OL,12,Fcommunity.
OL,14,F"What Labour must realise is the
OL,15,Fprecedent that the Tory veto set. It
OL,16,Fhas had real consequences, denying
OL,17,Fhard-won rights, fanning the flames of
OL,18,Fa reactionary culture war and paving
OL,19,Fthe way for other rights to be
OL,20,Freversed in other areas."
